“Viamala” (MS VIII; 
                    Poems [1891]; 
                    Works [1903])—Ruskin 
                    lists this title in his Plan for Continuation of the Account of a Tour on the Continent 
                    on the back endpapers of MS VIII. The title is the second in what can be interpreted as a definable cluster within the list, 
                    which constructs the experience of crossing the Alps:
